{"tid":1634854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"代出post 香港抗爭者誓詞","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:56:44.000Z","uid":7358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca5715ae53f434d486a129d57aefeb2845d6f50a","tid":1634854,"uid":7358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"撘上撘代出post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誓詞的目的其實很天真而且簡單，以最近局勢而論，只希望進一步能時刻提醒自己和其他抗爭者所做的一切，一定要跟極權政府，藍絲，黑警，黑社會所做的不一樣，亦用以對比黑警誓詞的荒謬，所有行動應以俠義精神為本，以公義為先。(講L完)<br />\n<br />\n誓詞全文：<br />\n<br />\n本人（姓名)，謹以至誠作出宣言 / 向全能之主發誓<br />\n本人將竭誠為香港之民主、自由、公義效力為反極權抗爭者<br />\n以俠義為本，儆惡懲奸，不畏懼，不徇私，不姦淫擄掠<br />\n不對街坊老幼懷惡意，不作無故破壞攻擊<br />\n忠誠行使逆權公民之權利<br />\n執行捍衞我城之職責，不篤灰，不割蓆<br />\n毫不懷疑地履行對抗暴政並合乎公義之行動<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQfAMCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQfAMCZ.jpg&h=a6329828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SK2jtRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSK2jtRm.jpg&h=f611ebc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"564bc800f692d41550bc165237b91183cfd2f6d1","tid":1634854,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文見此：<br />\n<br />\n【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家一定要繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"ef35ae674eadbb6a08ca1ac5aed30bc821dc7721","tid":1634854,"uid":7358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"697e64d58d32646bc6501b92071e919884450e9e","tid":1634854,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: